{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-recipe-post-js","path":"/番茄虾仁意面/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"一本食谱"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"1ce07b86-612b-5056-a73a-2247a09dc26b","excerpt":"食材 2 人份 意面 材料 量 备注 意面 200g 每人 100g 橄榄油、盐 少量 煮意面时加在水里 意面酱 材料 量 备注 虾仁 12 只  番茄 2 个  洋葱 0.3 个  蒜末 少量 可以用大蒜粉代替 胡椒 少量  罗勒叶 少量  意面酱 3-…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/a-cookbook/static/343b6eeab0c24f4bd6492570969dc716/9568a/image.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92.40506329113923%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"番茄虾仁意面\"\n        title=\"番茄虾仁意面\"\n        src=\"/a-cookbook/static/343b6eeab0c24f4bd6492570969dc716/828fb/image.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/a-cookbook/static/343b6eeab0c24f4bd6492570969dc716/ff44c/image.jpg 158w,\n/a-cookbook/static/343b6eeab0c24f4bd6492570969dc716/a6688/image.jpg 315w,\n/a-cookbook/static/343b6eeab0c24f4bd6492570969dc716/828fb/image.jpg 630w,\n/a-cookbook/static/343b6eeab0c24f4bd6492570969dc716/0ede0/image.jpg 945w,\n/a-cookbook/static/343b6eeab0c24f4bd6492570969dc716/3ac88/image.jpg 1260w,\n/a-cookbook/static/343b6eeab0c24f4bd6492570969dc716/9568a/image.jpg 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>食材</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2 人份</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h5>意面</h5>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">材料</th>\n<th align=\"left\">量</th>\n<th align=\"left\">备注</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">意面</td>\n<td align=\"left\">200g</td>\n<td align=\"left\">每人 100g</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">橄榄油、盐</td>\n<td align=\"left\">少量</td>\n<td align=\"left\">煮意面时加在水里</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h5>意面酱</h5>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">材料</th>\n<th align=\"left\">量</th>\n<th align=\"left\">备注</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">虾仁</td>\n<td align=\"left\">12 只</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">番茄</td>\n<td align=\"left\">2 个</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">洋葱</td>\n<td align=\"left\">0.3 个</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">蒜末</td>\n<td align=\"left\">少量</td>\n<td align=\"left\">可以用大蒜粉代替</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">胡椒</td>\n<td align=\"left\">少量</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">罗勒叶</td>\n<td align=\"left\">少量</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">意面酱</td>\n<td align=\"left\">3-4 勺</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>步骤</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>先开始煮意面</li>\n<li>煮的同时去炒意面酱</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>煮意面</h5>\n<ol>\n<li>水烧开放入意面</li>\n<li>加橄榄油、盐</li>\n<li>煮 10 ～ 20 分钟左右<em>（时间根据不同的意面定）</em></li>\n</ol>\n<h5>炒意面酱</h5>\n<ol>\n<li>虾仁焯水备用</li>\n<li>番茄、洋葱切丁备用</li>\n<li>热油炒番茄、洋葱、蒜末</li>\n<li>加意面酱、胡椒、罗勒叶，放入虾仁</li>\n<li>加水，盖上锅盖煮 5 ～ 8 分钟</li>\n<li>出锅前，加盐调味</li>\n</ol>\n<h5>完成</h5>\n<ol>\n<li>意面滤干水盛出，浇上意面酱</li>\n<li>撒上芝士和胡椒粉</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>备注</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>洋葱切得小的话，可以少煮一会儿</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"番茄虾仁意面","date":"August 24, 2022","description":"","contributors":["Yicheng"],"tags":["西餐","意面","虾","主食"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/大蒜子牛肉粒/大蒜子牛肉粒/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"大蒜子牛肉粒"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/牛油果吐司/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"牛油果吐司"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"1ce07b86-612b-5056-a73a-2247a09dc26b","previousPostId":"0c4f27b9-0f10-5786-9c30-b6902ee3308b","nextPostId":"0ab540ee-19d9-5334-805e-7fc52da9f706"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2297725318","2841359383"]}